            <title>[RAVE-378] User Prefs Demo for gadgets with localhost</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/RAVE-378</link>
                <project id="12311290" key="RAVE">Rave</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a gadget have &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8080&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8080&lt;/a&gt; in the Location and you want to update widget it gives URL is malformed&lt;/p&gt;</description>
